<p>
<note n="0769008" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0769008">天梵＝梵天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0769009" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0769009">如＋（是）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0769010" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0769010">〔等〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0770002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0770002">生＋（於有增上）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0770003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0770003">〔謂〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0770004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0770004">無＋（漏）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0770005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0770005">〔彼〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
