<note n="0772003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0772003">今＝令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0772004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0772004">眾＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
